An additional ''Micron'' MT29F2G08ABAEAH4-IT:E (256MB) Flash chip :(FBGA code NQ283) is located on the back of the board. The [[Quantenna]] radio has its own [[Samsung]] K482G1646F-BCMA (256MB) RAM chip. :A 2TB ''Seagate'' Video 3.5" HDD pictured in the FCC internal photos. Another device contained a 2TB ''WD'' GreenPower 3.5" HDD.
